Always run tests from the project root dir.
After any file update, always run:

hatch run style    # Black + Ruff checks  
hatch run typing   # MyPy type checking
hatch run test test/test_capture/ -v  # Integration tests and misc tests
hatch run test-capture                # Unit tests for the hunyo-capture package
hatch run test-mcp                    # Unit tests for the hunyo-mcp-server package